{
  "id": "fleet-management-onboarding",
  "title": "Fleet Management: Onboard Your First Collector",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "In this guide, you'll deploy and connect a Grafana Alloy collector to Fleet Management. By the end, you'll have a running collector visible in your inventory."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "id": "setup-terminal",
      "title": "Set up terminal",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "terminal-connect",
          "content": "First, connect to a terminal session. This is where you'll run the Alloy deployment command."
        },
        {
          "type": "terminal",
          "command": "docker ps",
          "content": "Verify the terminal is working by running a quick command.",
          "requirements": [
            "is-terminal-active"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "With the terminal ready, you'll generate a token and deploy Alloy using the Fleet Management UI."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "id": "deploy-collector",
      "title": "Deploy a collector",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-collector-app/fleet-management']",
          "requirements": [
            "navmenu-open"
          ],
          "content": "Open **Fleet Management** from the main menu."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='tab-fleet-inventory']",
          "content": "Select the **Inventory** tab."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "The Inventory tab shows all connected collectors. You'll now generate a token and get the deployment command for a new collector."
        },
        {
          "type": "guided",
          "content": "Generate a token and copy the deployment command.",
          "stepTimeout": 60000,
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button[data-testid='fleet-inventory-add-collector-button']",
              "tooltip": "Opens the collector setup dialog",
              "skippable": true
            },
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input[data-testid='generate-token-name-input']",
              "targetvalue": "new-token",
              "tooltip": "Enter a name to identify this token",
              "skippable": true
            },
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button[data-testid='generate-token-submit-button']",
              "tooltip": "Creates the token",
              "skippable": true
            },
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button:contains(\"Copy to clipboard\"):nth-match(2)",
              "tooltip": "Copies the deployment command",
              "skippable": true
            },
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button[aria-label=\"Close\"]",
              "tooltip": "Close the dialog when done"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[aria-label='Expand terminal']",
          "content": "Expand the terminal panel.",
          "tooltip": "Opens the terminal at full height",
          "skippable": true
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "canvas.xterm-link-layer:nth-of-type(1)",
          "content": "Paste the deployment command and press **Enter**.",
          "tooltip": "Right-click or Ctrl+V to paste",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "terminal",
          "command": "sudo systemctl status alloy",
          "content": "Check that Alloy is running.",
          "requirements": [
            "is-terminal-active"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "The collector is now deployed. Head back to the inventory to confirm it appears."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "id": "verify-collector",
      "title": "Verify your collector",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "navigate",
          "reftarget": "/a/grafana-collector-app/fleet-management/fleet-inventory",
          "content": "Return to the **Fleet Inventory**. Refresh the page if needed."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "div[data-testid^=\"collector-row-\"]:nth-match(1)",
          "content": "Select your collector to view its status and details.",
          "tooltip": "Shows connection status and configuration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "Your collector is now connected to Fleet Management. From here you can push configurations, monitor health, and manage collectors at scale."
    }
  ]
}
